Company Description: Founded in 1930, Alta Loma Psychological Associates specializes in individual, group and family therapy services. It maintains a staff of more than 10 employees, including therapists, psychoanalysts and psychiatrists. The center provides treatment services for patients with depression, anxiety, relationship problems, eating disorders, marital conflict, job crises, and drug and alcohol abuse. Alta Loma Psychological Associates offers consulting, anger and stress management and weight control services. It also provides services to rape victims and prevents crimes and domestic violence. Additionally, the center offers workers' compensation, psychiatric evaluations and therapy services. Alta Loma Psychological Associates provides parenting services that deters parent and children conflicts. It is located in Rancho Cucamonga, Calif.

Company Description: California Mentor offers a wide range of community-based services to adults and children with developmental disabilities, brain injury and elders in need of home care. It also offers services for children and adolescents with emotional, behavioral and medically complex challenges. The company is operated by The MENTOR Network, a national network of local human services providers that was founded in 1980. The network offers human services professionals specializing in accounting and financial reporting and cutting-edge clinical systems. It is a member of various national organizations, including the Foster Family-Based Treatment Association, American Network of Community Options and Resources and Brain Injury Association of America. California Mentor is located in Rancho Cucamonga, Calif.
